{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI 사용자를 위한 비즈보드 광고를 탬플릿 형식으로 제공합니다."}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"AdFitSDK"}],"title":"비즈보드 광고 연동 for SwiftUI","role":"article","images":[{"identifier":"banner-card.png","type":"card"},{"identifier":"iphone.png","type":"icon"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK\/SwiftUI+BannerAd"],"generated":true}],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK","doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK\/Simple+SwiftUI"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK\/SwiftUI+BizBoardTemplate"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"bizBoardSample.jpeg"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"비즈보드 광고는 배너 형태의 네이티브 요소로 구성된 광고입니다."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"웹뷰가 아닌 네이티브 UI를 사용하여 광고가 노출되고 있습니다."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"1. 광고 생성하기","anchor":"1-%EA%B4%91%EA%B3%A0-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0"},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"title":"SwiftUI","content":[{"type":"codeListing","code":["import SwiftUI","import AdFitSDK","","struct ContentView: View {","    @State var isRefresh: Bool = false","","    var body: some View {","        BizBoardTemplatePresentableView(","            clientId: \"발급받은 광고 단위 ID를 입력해 주세요.\",","            refresh: $isRefresh","        )","        \/\/ 광고가 보여질 때마다 갱신처리 됩니다.","        .onAppear {","            isRefresh = true","        }","        .onDisappear {","            isRefresh = false","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"발급받은 광고 단위를 입력하면, 광고 뷰가 생성됩니다. (광고 호출에 관한 부분은 생성과 동시에 호출되고, 내부적으로 제어됩니다.)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"2-operator-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0","type":"heading","text":"2. operator 설정하기","level":2},{"tabs":[{"content":[{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["public func onDidReceiveAd(_ closure: ((AdFitSDK.AdFitNativeAd) -> Void)?) -> AdFitSDK.BizBoardTemplatePresentableView"]}],"title":"SwiftUI"}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"네이티브 광고가 성공적으로 로드되었을 때 호출됩니다.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"parameter closure: 광고가 로드되었을 때, 호출되는 closure","type":"text"}]}]}]}]}],"type":"row","numberOfColumns":1},{"tabs":[{"title":"SwiftUI","content":[{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["public func onDidFailToReceiveAd(_ closure: ((Error) -> Void)?) -> AdFitSDK.BizBoardTemplatePresentableView"]}]}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"네이티브 광고 로드에 실패한 경우 호출됩니다.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"parameter closure: 광고가 로드에 실패했을 때, 호출되는 closure"}]}]}]}]}],"type":"row","numberOfColumns":1},{"tabs":[{"content":[{"code":["public func onDidClickAd(_ closure: ((AdFitSDK.AdFitNativeAd) -> Void)?) -> AdFitSDK.BizBoardTemplatePresentableView"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"title":"SwiftUI"}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"columns":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"네이티브 광고에서 사용자 클릭이 발생하였을 때 호출됩니다."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"클릭에 의해 광고주 페이지가 전체 화면으로 노출되므로, 화면 전환 시 필요한 동작이 있다면 이 메서드에 구현하세요.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"parameter closure: 클릭 이벤트가 발생했을 때, 호출되는 closure"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"size":1}],"type":"row","numberOfColumns":1},{"tabs":[{"title":"SwiftUI","content":[{"syntax":"swift","code":["public func onSizeThatFits() -> some View"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"디바이스의 width를 기준으로 광고 비율을 계산하여 비즈보드 광고 뷰의 사이즈를 설정해 주는 operator입니다.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"note: 이 operator를 사용할 경우, padding이나 추가적인 사이즈 설정을 하지 않아야 광고가 노출됩니다."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}]}],"type":"row","numberOfColumns":1}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/adfitsdk\/swiftui+bizboardtemplate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"ad-icon.png":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/AdFitSDK\/ad-icon@2x.png","traits":["2x","light"]}],"alt":"A technology icon representing the SlothCreator framework.","identifier":"ad-icon.png"},"bizBoardSample.jpeg":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/AdFitSDK\/bizBoardSample.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"bizBoardSample.jpeg","type":"image","alt":"비즈보드 탬플릿"},"banner-card.png":{"alt":"배너 광고 카드","variants":[{"traits":["2x","light"],"url":"\/images\/AdFitSDK\/banner-card@2x.png"}],"identifier":"banner-card.png","type":"image"},"doc://AdFitSDK/documentation/AdFitSDK/Simple+SwiftUI":{"title":"AdFitSDK SwiftUI 지원","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"SwiftUI 기반 프로젝트에서의 연동 방법을 소개합니다.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/adfitsdk\/simple+swiftui","role":"collectionGroup","identifier":"doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK\/Simple+SwiftUI","kind":"article","images":[{"identifier":"banner-card.png","type":"card"},{"identifier":"iphone.png","type":"icon"}]},"iphone.png":{"alt":"A technology icon representing the SlothCreator framework.","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/AdFitSDK\/iphone.png"}],"identifier":"iphone.png","type":"image"},"doc://AdFitSDK/documentation/AdFitSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/adfitsdk","kind":"symbol","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ad-icon.png"}],"title":"AdFitSDK","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"AdFit SDK","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/AdFit